      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project with this budget-friendly find! This car is in poor condition and will require some significant mechanical and cosmetic work to get back in top shape, but it's the perfect canvas for a restorer or anyone looking for a low-cost entry into their next vehicle. It\u2019s an honest, affordable opportunity for someone who loves to bring a car back to life!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
