    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the pinnacle of care and preservation. The exterior paint retains its original showroom luster with absolutely no scratches, dents, or imperfections, while the interior is immaculate, smelling fresh and showing zero wear on the premium upholstery. Mechanically, the car is flawless; the engine performs with whisper-quiet precision, and every electronic feature and safety system functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Complete with a full service history and having been garage-kept its entire life, this car offers a rare opportunity for a buyer seeking a like-new experience.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in 'poor' condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently faces significant mechanical challenges, including a persistent engine misfire and a transmission that requires professional attention. The exterior shows its age with visible rust on the body panels, significant paint oxidation, and multiple dents. Inside, the cabin requires a deep clean and repair, as the upholstery is heavily worn and several power features are currently inoperable. This car is best suited as a dedicated project for an enthusiast or as a donor vehicle for parts.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
